'''Hamilton Dhlamini''' (wavutse ku ya 15 Ukuboza 1969), rimwe na rimwe nka '''Hamilton Dlamini''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]], umwanditsi w'amakinamico ndetse n'umukinnyi wa filime . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime na ''teleserial Isithembiso'', ''[[:en:Faith_like_Potatoes|Faith like Potatoes]]  The King's Messenger''. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/Celebs/i-go-to-shebeens-and-places-that-are-considered-dangerous-to-build-my-characters-hamilton-dlamini-on-his-badboy-characters-20180622</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 15 Ukuboza 1969 mu mudugudu wo mu cyaro i Sebokeng, muri [[Afurika y'Epfo]] mu muryango ufite ubukungu bubi. <ref name="dlamini">https://briefly.co.za/39553-hamilton-dlamini-biography-age-wife-family-voice-hometown-tv-shows-movies-awards-instagram.html</ref>

Yashakanye ninzobere mu mirire, Martha, aho bafitanye abana batatu. Yabanje guhura na Marita muri lift. <ref>https://zalebs.com/relationships/hamilton-dlamini/isithembisos-hamilton-dlamini-shares-how-he-met-his-wife</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wo gukina mu ntangiriro za 1984 abinyujije mu ikinamico. Yakinnye kandi nk'umucuruzi muri Koreya muri SABC 1 sitcom ''Mzee Wa Two Six'' . Mu ntangiriro za 2008, yagize uruhare runini mu biganiro bigufi kuri SABC1, byahujwe ''n’ikinamico ya King'' Shakespeare ya William Shakespeare . <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=4045</ref> Nanone, yakinnye cyane kuri SABC 2 sitcom ''Stokvel'' hamwe n <nowiki>'' Mojo Khumalo '</nowiki>.  Muri 2008, yakinnye muri serie ''Ten Bush'' iyobowe na Mncedisi Shabangu. Ku ruhare rwe, nyuma yaje gutsindira igihembo cya Naledi Theatre igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza. Hanyuma muri 2009, yakoranye na William Kentridge hamwe na Handspring Puppet Company kuri ''Woyzeck muri Highveld'' . <ref name="dlami">https://www.theheadandtheload.com/hd-bio</ref>

Muri 2006, yakinnye muri firime ya Regardt van den Bergh ''Kwizera nk'ibirayi'' . Kuri iyi nshuro, yatsindiye ibihembo bya Filime na Televiziyo byo muri Afurika yepfo (Safta) kubera umukinnyi ushyigikiye neza uruhare rwe. <ref name="dlami">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.theheadandtheload.com/hd-bio "HAMILTON DLAMINI"]. theheadandtheload<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Muri 2007, yatsindiye igihembo cya Zahabu  kubera Umukinnyi witwaye neza muri Filime. Muri 2018, yakinnye 'Banzi Motaung' muri televiziyo izwi cyane ''Isithembiso'' . Muri uwo mwaka, yongeye gutsindira igihembo cya Golden Horn igihembo cyumukinnyi mwiza muri opera yisabune ya TV 'Isithembiso'.  <ref name="tvsa">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=4045 "Bio"]. tvsa<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Yashinze kandi uruganda rwe rukora ibicuruzwa, 'Ndlondlo Productions'. <ref name="dlami">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.theheadandtheload.com/hd-bio "HAMILTON DLAMINI"]. theheadandtheload<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

